'''Coleman Townsend Robinson''' (12 January 1838 – 1 May 1872) was an American [[entomologist]] who specialised in [[Lepidoptera]].
He wrote Grote, A.R., & Robinson, C.T. 1867–1868. Descriptions of American Lepidoptera – Nos 1–3. ''Transactions of the [[American Entomological Society]]'' 1(1): 1–30; (2): 171–192, pl. 4; (4): 323–360, pl. 6, pl. 7 with [[Augustus Radcliffe Grote]].
